      <accessrestrict id="aspace_85219b4f6f442490aaee7f16fade7edc">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>
         <p>Original audiotape, videotape, and motion picture films, as well as preservation masters and duplicating masters, may not be played. Researchers needing to consult the original materials should refer to the finding aid for policies governing reproduction for access.</p>  
