      <scopecontent id="aspace_d2bc5a8a1cf84d722dc09a15b7129d27">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Collier W. Baird Collection contains the film, "Lucky Lindbergh," which documents Charles Lindbergh's departure from and return to the United States during the first nonstop solo flight across the Atlantic Ocean in 1927.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
  
